10516:+summaryLines.push(`The cohort shows a strong multivariable signal for pfs_months. Main effects explain substantial variation (R^2=${round(1 - allMainModel.rss / yCenteredSS, 6)}), and adding the leading interaction candidates increases R^2 to ${round(jointInteractions.r2, 6)}. The most clinically interpretable pattern is not a single marker alone but heterogeneity around feature_046: its favorable association with pfs_months is reduced in feature_031=1 and feature_063=1 contexts, increased in feature_069=1 contexts, and coupled with a stronger adverse feature_062 slope. The apparent feature_010 enhancement was not robust in the joint interaction model.`);
